metadata.name: The Salamander
metadata.description:
Once upon a time some titan stole from the gods and brought us closer to the most mysterious nymphs: The Salamanders... I always need them to activate the rest of elements, they are dancers and have the power of the present that breaks every hex.

Since I was a child I was raised by nymphs, they talk to me and care for me. Some reptilians fed off my fears in the shadows, but the fire was ignited and now I can fly.

Think on this: what really means flagrant?
